HEADWORD: Unremitting
<hw>Un`re*mit"ting</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not remitting;
incessant; continued; persevering; <as>as, <ex>unremitting</ex>
exertions</as>.</def> <au>Cowper.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Un`re*mit"ting*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un`re*mit"ting*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unremorseless</ent>⟦br⟧
